author: jleroux
msg: Fix for OFBIZ-3832, adding a forum entry causes an illegal argument exception.  The problem was that one of the parameters passed to a Math.min(int, int) call was actually a String and the call-class-method doesn't attempt to convert arguments, it possibly should but I didn't change that here.
